'''騎士視界'''（Knightscope），或稱「K5[[原型_(工程)|原型]]測試版」（K5 beta prototype），是一個全{{link-en|自主機器人|Autonomous robot}}（Autonomous robot），由位於[[美國|美國]][[矽谷|矽谷]]的同名公司所開發。它被設計用於[[學校|學校]]、[[企業|企業]]、[[社區|社區]]的[[犯罪|犯罪]]預防工作<ref name=VOA>{{cite news|author1=李艾琳|title=机器警察执法 威慑犯罪活动|url=http://www.voachinese.com/content/robot-security-20150602/2805421.html|accessdate=2015-06-03|agency=[[美國之音|美國之音]]|date=2015-06-03|archive-date=2015-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150603213630/http://www.voachinese.com/content/robot-security-20150602/2805421.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Daily Mail">{{cite news | url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2516662/The-dawn-REAL-Robocop-Machines-armed-thermal-imaging-radar-cameras-designers-say-help-prevent-Sandy-Hook.html | title=The dawn of a REAL Robocop? | publisher=Daily Mail | work=The dawn of a REAL Robocop? | accessdate=2 December 2013 | location=London | date=2 December 2013 | archive-date=2015-09-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924180956/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2516662/The-dawn-REAL-Robocop-Machines-armed-thermal-imaging-radar-cameras-designers-say-help-prevent-Sandy-Hook.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="New York Times">{{cite news | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/12/03/science/coming-soon-a-night-watchman-with-wheels.html?_r=0 | title=A Night Watchman With Wheels? | publisher=New York Times | work=A Night Watchman With Wheels? | accessdate=2 December 2013 | first=John | last=Markoff | date=29 November 2013 | archive-date=2015-09-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905170627/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/12/03/science/coming-soon-a-night-watchman-with-wheels.html?_r=0 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="FOX News">{{cite news | url=http://www.foxnews.com/tech/2013/12/01/300-pound-robot-is-new-breed-crime-fighting-machine/ | title=300-pound robot is new breed of crime-fighting machine | publisher=FOX News | work=300-pound robot is new breed of crime-fighting machine | date=1 December 2013 | accessdate=2 December 2013 | archive-date=2015-05-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150520020957/http://www.foxnews.com/tech/2013/12/01/300-pound-robot-is-new-breed-crime-fighting-machine/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。開發商表示，設計此機器人的動機與[[靈感|靈感]]是源自於[[桑迪·胡克小学枪击案|桑迪·胡克小学枪击案]]，希望這種機器人能用於預防未來可能的犯罪<ref name="Daily Mail" /><ref name="New York Times" /><ref name="FOX News" /> 。機器人有5[[英尺|英尺]]高，和300磅重。K5用於預防犯罪的[[传感器|传感器]]包括有{{link-en|視訊攝影機|video camera}}、[[热成像仪|热成像仪]]、[[激光测距仪|激光测距仪]]、小型[[雷达|雷达]]、空氣品質传感器（air quality sensor）和[[麥克風|麥克風]]等。如果偵測到異常的噪音與溫度變化，或已知的[[罪犯|罪犯]]，它會自動通知當地執法當局<ref name="New York Times" /><ref name="FOX News" />。

